                        <div id="M13_B_DB_Movie_OverviewAboveMovieCommentTG">            </div>        </div>    </div>	</div></div></div>    <div class="db_i_comcont">        <div class="db_i_comment">                        <div id="ratingDownRegion"></div>                                                <div id="M13_B_DB_Movie_OverviewAboveHotMovieCommentTG">            </div>            <div class="clearfix db_comcont new_comcont">                <p class="line_solid left" id="reviewLineLeft"> </p>                <p class="line_solid right" id="reviewLineRight"> </p>                <div class="main">                                                                                
<div id="reviewRegion" class="db_longcom">
    <h4>长影评</h4>
    <div class="longcombox">
        <dl>
    <dt class="__r_c_" pan="M14_Movie_Overview_LongReview_1"><span>TOP</span><strong>1</strong></dt>
    <dd class="__r_c_" pan="M14_Movie_Overview_LongReview_1">
        <h3><a target="_blank" href="http://movie.mtime.com/157155/reviews/7981621.html">赏色为主，猎奇为辅</a></h3>
    </dd>
    <dd class="clearfix mt20 __r_c_" pan="M14_Movie_Overview_LongReview_1">
        <div class="comboxcont clearfix">
        蒂姆·波顿的电影，一言以蔽之，就是诡异与童真，用个比较奇怪的名词“哥特童话”形容也可以。

 

